metadata.exif:ImageDescription: A supporter of the Mexican Electricians Union (SME) confronts Mexican policemen, at the building where the company is located and that was confiscated by the Government in 2009, , in Mexico City, Mexico, on 11 April 2011. In the vicinity of the Federal Electricity Commission (CFE), the protesters set fire to at least four vehicles and disrupted traffic.
